rComments: I have quite literally NEVER met a professor so absurd and so blatantly uncaring for his students or their welfare. Gilles refused to post slides or notes online in order for us to look over to study. He doesn't have slides to show DURING lectures either and chooses to drone on and on about tangents that are wildly irrelevant to the course.

I love this prof he doesn't mark anything and its russian roulette for what you'll get. He never gives clear guidelines for anything at all so you'll never know what you're going to get. If you're going to class make sure to pay attention because he will call on you. He also hates the university and will always come late.

Levasseur is a genious. Bottom line end of story. He told us that we didn't need to buy are textbooks, all we had to do was take notes. If you have him for orgnizational communication, write down his stories/examples, pay attentions to what he says, and participate in his improvised debates, he'll remember you come marking season.
I've never even heard of a professor this bad.  I mean it.
This guy is hilarious! Sure he was a bit hard to follow but it was worth coming to class just to hear his stories!!!!
You will not believe he is actually a prof.
